                            <comment id="13036783" author="fertapric" created="Fri, 20 May 2011 12:28:25 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;Patch&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13041996" author="mk" created="Wed, 1 Jun 2011 07:22:48 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks for the patch.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The patch works great, except that it doesn&apos;t create the proper indexes on the mongoMapCollection.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Default mongoMapCollection = &quot;mongo_data_model_map&quot;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Adding the following will increase performance exponentially:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;db.mongo_data_model_map.ensureIndex(&lt;/p&gt;
{element_id : 1}
&lt;p&gt;)&lt;br/&gt;
db.mongo_data_model_map.ensureIndex(&lt;/p&gt;
{long_value : 1}
&lt;p&gt;)&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13042036" author="fertapric" created="Wed, 1 Jun 2011 09:12:44 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks for the tip Mike. I just uploaded the new patch implementing the indexes thingy.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
